{"type":null,"faqId":21081,"title":"省电小窍门","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>不使用手机时，按电源键关闭屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>缩短屏幕休眠时间：在主屏幕，设置 &gt; 显示 &gt; 休眠，设置屏幕休眠时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>降低屏幕亮度：在主屏幕， &gt; 设置 &gt; 显示 &gt; 亮度，设置屏幕亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>关闭蓝牙和WLAN：在主屏幕， &gt; 设置，在无线和网络区域关闭蓝牙和WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>关闭后台数据同步：在主屏幕， &gt; 设置 &gt; 账户，关闭帐户与同步。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>关闭数据业务：在主屏幕， &gt; 设置 &gt; 更多… &gt; 移动网络，取消勾选已启用数据流量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>关闭GPS：在主屏幕， &gt; 设置 &gt; 位置服务，取消勾选GPS卫星。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4744","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1426837645000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-CL00,Pine-CL10,Pine-TL00M,Pine-TL10,Pine-TL20,Pine-UL00","visitedTimes":213,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}